Connection with the AC Mobile Control gateway failed.

Checklist:
1. do you have active network connection (WiFi and/or 3G);
2. the air conditioning system is powered;
3. AC Mobile Control gateway is properly installed and configured;
4. the AC Mobile Control application is configured to work with AC Mobile Control gateway;
5. you have selected connection method proper for your location (home network or remote access).


If you are trying to connect remotely: The correct operation of this function requires a static and public IP address and the correct configuration of the home router. In order to verify the possibility of remote access, contact your Internet Service Provider (ISP). 

